{"tid":1109632,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"「連登公投」今次單野馬國明慘啲定鄭秀文慘啲？","createTime":"2019-04-16T10:28:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-16T12:37:27.000Z","uid":5006,"like":14,"dislike":100,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"e0dc52f301a86daa7dbbc6bc96c781158a3b53cc","tid":1109632,"uid":5006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T10:28:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />馬國明慘啲：<br />\n全城見證帶綠帽，屋企人都比記者搞。仲要夜晚繼續返工，面對同事同劇組人員，關心你又唔知點應，唔理你又明知大家扮緊無野，果堆同事隨時背後笑緊自己...仲要起鏡頭面前扮開心/借機大喊一場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />鄭秀文慘啲：<br />\n好唔容易先起抑鬱症好返黎，信教重整人生，又老鼠安歷經好多患難先結婚，黃子華都拎過黎吹奏，以為重返光明。仲要同賓穎做過gym同自拍，好似比朋友同愛人同時背叛，即刻落返地獄咁款<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3abf398e8d9ebf9960f43c949bbfbea86f4eabfa","tid":1109632,"uid":2419,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T10:28:53.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">HK01抄POST死全家</span>"},{"pid":"3012e29c835c7c4e0af7ff44458bd6c62c65f956","tid":1109632,"uid":5077,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T10:29:28.000Z","msg":"咁都仲要鬥慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22b372dc03d91cd50a4c0d63a555caa2e0cf644b","tid":1109632,"uid":5006,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"3012e29c835c7c4e0af7ff44458bd6c62c65f956","tid":1109632,"uid":5077,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T10:29:28.000Z","msg":"咁都仲要鬥慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T10:30:42.000Z","msg":"真 &middot; 鬥慘大會"},{"pid